c: 7
v: 95
t: "Paﾅ淌ｪ me (temtﾃｪla wan) guhurand; me di ﾅ淌ｻna sikatﾃｮyan qencﾃｮ dane wan, heya ewan (ji wan tengayan) fereste bﾃｻne ﾃｻ (aha) gotine: \"Bi sond! Bi bav ﾃｻ bapﾃｮrﾃｪn me da jﾃｮ tengasﾃｮ ﾃｻ firetﾃｮ (mirﾃｻz ﾃｻ ﾅ歛yﾃｮ) hatibﾃｻye (ewan jﾃｮ evan royﾃｪn hanﾃｪnan dﾃｮtine).\" ﾃ仕ﾃｮ (ewan bi van dilxwazﾃｮyan mane, hemﾃｻ tiﾅ殳 bﾃｮrva kirine) haja wan qe ji wan ne maye, me ewan niﾅ殘ﾃｪ va (bi ﾅ歛patan) girtin"